{"type": "article", "id": 22448, "title": "实验室风格的吊灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-02-18T07:30:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 24, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607122231p2lH8eAIXhstrBOq.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">瑞典灯具品牌 wästberg 在家具展上带来了一款 w162 dalston 照明灯，由 industrial facility 设计。这款灯的外形是仓库或工作室里最常见的一种，但就是这样看似简单的灯非常坚固耐用。灯罩有金属或玻璃两种，可安装 LED 灯，不同色彩组合在一起后有独特的艺术感。<a href=\"http://www.industrialfacility.co.uk/page/projects/lighting/dalston-lamp\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122229BlIc5QA07jZWKGts.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122229BTmZwkKpNYMQElWS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60268949\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222305nBS8ueTfG0ljoXO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65281174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122230HVE0Gxv7adFPtu3j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67481663\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122230he6ZL0qRsG9xXFpB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66381418\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><br></p>\n\n\n"}